<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1078685/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078686" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo atque Incomparabili
                <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Quoniam hac hebdomada responsum, uti sperabam,
            <lb/>ad meas <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> ultima pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teriti Augusti datas non accepi,
            <lb/>unam adhuc ad te mittere epistolam non abs re
            <lb/>fore judico adhoc ut si forte fortuna <rs key="B_1714-08-31_991170515019805501" type="letter">prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                <lb/>me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, 31. August 1714.</note> per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> amandat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> perierint, saltem h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c, quod
            <lb/>per <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs> mitto ad Tuas perveniat Manus.
            <lb/><choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> D. D. Patavini <rs type="organisation">Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>
<lb/>responsum Tuum Vir Doctissime expectant, nec non
            <lb/>scire cupiunt num <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> discessurus, Patriamque
            <lb/>derelicturus sis <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> veniendi gratia ad
            <lb/>Mathematicas disciplinas edocendas, salario 1500 Tha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lerorum imperialium annuatim Tibi persoluto.
            <lb/>Ego revera ipsis Nobilissimis <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs> Tui obti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nendi spem aliquam feci, si annuatim persolvere
            <lb/>velint 1500 Thaleros imperiales hoc est totidem
            <lb/>uncias argenti; hancque spem deduxi ex humanissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma Tua <rs key="B_1714-07-18_991170515020205501" type="letter">epistola</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti vom 18. Juli 1714.</note> 18 Iulii exarata, in qua scripsisti
            <lb/>Vir Celeberrime Te ne quidem permotum iri oblat<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
            <lb/>summa minori quam 1500 Thalerorum imperialium
            <lb/>hoc est totidem unciarum argenti. Copiam <rs key="B_1714-07-18_991170515020205501" type="letter">littera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum</rs> Tuarum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Proceribus</rs> meis Amplissimis dedi; ipsi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que stipendium 1500 Thalerorum imperialium quod
            <lb/>petivisti exhibent, atque annuatim persolvent: quare
            <pb facs="1078687" n="1v"/>
<lb/>reliquum est ut Tu Vir <choice><sic>Clarissme</sic><corr>Clarissime</corr></choice> sine mora <rs key="B_1714-10-20_991170515019305501" type="letter">litteris
                <lb/>Tuis iucundissimis</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli gibt Antwort in seinem Brief vom 20. Oktober 1714.</note> me admonitum facias de tuo ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ventu, quem cum Proceribus meis, multisque aliis
            <lb/>Viris doctis ipse exopto. Uti dicebam in <rs key="B_1714-08-31_991170515019805501" type="letter">pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus
                <lb/>meis</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Johann I Bernoulli, 31. August 1714.</note> progressu temporis poteris substituere Agnatum
            <lb/>Tuum Doctissimum <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaum</rs> siquidem <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavina
                <lb/>Urbs</rs> non arriserit: C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m aer patavinus optimus
    <lb/>est, et temperamento tuo conducet. <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Veneti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> omnibus
            <lb/>iucundissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fortasse non displicebunt vacationum
            <lb/>tempore, quo cubiculum Domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sine expensis
            <lb/>Tibi semper paratum erit. Stipendium oblatum
            <lb/>1500 Thalerorum imperialium ne respuas rogo,
            <lb/>et vocationibus tam honorificis ne relucteris de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>precor saltem ne labores meis pro Vobis libentis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sime impensi evadant prorsus irriti et frustranei.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale et fave Vir omni virtutum genere pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissime.</salute>
<dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1714-09-23">23 Septembris 1714</date></dateline></closer>
<postscript><p>P. S. Salutem plurimam meo nomine dicito Illustrissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo Fratri tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Nicolao</rs> Status Vestri Consiliario, nec
            <lb/>non Clarissimo Agnato Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>. Quin Illustrissimus
            <lb/>Frater Tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Nicolaus</rs> meam acceperit <rs key="B_1714-08-31_991170517053105501" type="letter">epistolam</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Niklaus Bernoulli den Älteren vom 31. August 1714.</note>
<lb/>ei inclusam, quam ultima <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> transacti Augusti
            <pb facs="1078688" n="2r"/>
<lb/>per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> ad Te amandavi, haud ambigo.</p></postscript>
